<p>Making update to API AutoFlow is as simple as change the action settings. Which is a good news considering the industry average for software maintenance is around 60% of the total cost.</p>

<p>Letâ€™s say your customer wants to change the date format</p>

<p>2021/04/19  â€”â€”&gt;   2021-04-19 â€”â€“&gt; 20210419
Making the change
Simply go the String/replace action and remove the â€œ-â€ in the replacement setting</p>

